ET_2014_05_v0


==============================================================================

CHANGES FOR ET_2014_05_v0
=========================

Flesh
=====

1) Support for native Complex grid variables in both C99 and C++.
   Cactus' COMPLEX type now maps to the native complex types in these
   languages and the CCTK functions to manipulate them are deprecated:

     CCTK_Cmplx
     CCTK_CmplxReal
     CCTK_CmplxImag
     CCTK_CmplxConjg
     CCTK_CmplxAbs
     CCTK_CmplxAdd
     CCTK_CmplxSub
     CCTK_CmplxMul
     CCTK_CmplxDiv
     CCTK_CmplxSqrt
     CCTK_CmplxSin
     CCTK_CmplxCos
     CCTK_CmplxLog
     CCTK_CmplxExp


